OL,3,CMeet the 100-year-old driver who's
OL,4,Cbeen behind the wheel for 87 years
OL,6,FA 100-year-old driver from who's been
OL,7,Fbehind the wheel for 87 years says age
OL,8,Fis just a number.
OL,10,FEric Dixon started driving just before
OL,11,Fhe turned 14 and has since driven
OL,12,FHGVs, buses, coaches and cars.
OL,14,FHe's still motoring around in his Kia
OL,15,Fand believes someone's age does not
OL,16,Fimpact their ability.
OL,18,FHe said: "Don't judge people by their
OL,19,Fage, judge them by what they can do I
OL,20,Fthink that is far fairer.
