OL,3,CMeet the 100-year-old driver who's
OL,4,Cbeen behind the wheel for 87 years
OL,6,FShe described him as a "very
OL,7,Fcourteous" driver, adding: "I would
OL,8,Fsay a very careful driver he's not
OL,9,Fslow. He can put his foot down when he
OL,10,Fwants".
OL,12,FMr Dixon says he will know when it's
OL,13,Ftime to stop driving.
OL,15,FHe said: "I honestly feel that I will
OL,16,Fknow when the time is due to pack it
OL,17,Fin and I will.
OL,19,F"I've seen too much of other people
OL,20,Fwho shouldn't be driving. I don't want
OL,21,Fto be one of them."
