OL,3,CMeet the 100-year-old driver who's
OL,4,Cbeen behind the wheel for 87 years
OL,6,FDo you have to retake a driving test
OL,7,Fover a certain age?
OL,9,FDriving licences expire when you turn
OL,10,F70, but people can renew them every
OL,11,Fthree years if they want to carry on
OL,12,Fdriving.
OL,14,FAccording to the insurance company
OL,15,FRAC, drivers over 70 years old "won't
OL,16,Fhave to take another test and there's
OL,17,Fno upper age limit for driving".
OL,19,FDrivers who are still fit enough to
OL,20,Fdrive can continue doing so for as
OL,21,Flong as they want to.
